data.description:
Located in The Sentinels in beautiful Gray's Creek, this home has so much to offer!
Built in late 2021
With a HUGE living room, kitchen (look at that island and pantry!!), large fully fenced back yard, and a huge landing upstairs this home is sure to be one for entertaining! Especially with football season and holidays right around the corner!
Get cozy on the couch in front of the electric fireplace or enjoy the upcoming cool fall nights on the back patio while listening to the sounds of the country.
With a mix of easy going country and access to Hope Mills, Hwy 87, and I-95 plus 4 large bedrooms this home has it all!
Have a car lot for a driveway? Great! This home also has a large driveway and 3 car garage!
Enjoy working with your hands? Even better, look at that work bench!
Have a lot of clothes? Collect shoes or hand bags? That huge closet is your new best friend!

Come see for yourself before this beauty gets away!
